razak atunwa (born 17 october 1969) honourable speaker kwara state house of assembly, nigeria. he was a member of the ruling people's democratic party (pdp) between 2002 and 2014. on 22 january 2014 he formally announced his membership of the all progressives congress (apc). on 28 march 2015 he was elected as a member of the house of representatives to represent asa/ilorin west federal constituency.